Class ArrayVector

java.lang.Object
ArrayVector
All Implemented Interfaces:
BooleanVector
public class ArrayVector extends Object implements BooleanVector
An implementation of the Boolean Vector interface where the Boolean values are stored in an array of type boolean[].
